            <div class="xmltag" xmlattrs="{&quot;SUBTYPE&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" xmltagname="HEADING">NERVE CWRC Entry Test File - short, with pre-existing entity tags <div class="taggedentity" standard="Duncan, Sara Jeanette" xmlattrs="{&quot;STANDARD&quot;:&quot;Duncan, Sara Jeanette&quot;,&quot;REF&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" xmltagname="NAME" draggable="true" data-collection="">Duncan, Sara Jeanette</div>(1861-1922)</div> 
            <div class="xmltag" xmlattrs="{}" xmltagname="RESEARCHNOTE">
